description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a Paediatric Registered Nurse looking for a new challenge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a rewarding role where you can work 1:1 with a patient in their own home?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for experienced, committed, Paediatric Registered Nurses to support our service users with their complex care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our service user is a young girl who has a rare and complex genetic condition, which means she requires the 1:1 support of an experienced Paediatric Nurse to manage her care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;She is a happy young girl who enjoys spending time with her family, she communicates by using different sounds to indicate her mood.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal applicant will hold a valid NMC PIN and have experience in either children&#39;s or adults nursing and can evidence hands-on clinical care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is essential for you to be able to commit to regular hours for continuity of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Current NMC PIN&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Paediatric Nursing experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Ventilation Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Oxygen Monitoring&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Oral suctioning&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Gastrostomy Care&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have the following shifts available;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Night shifts from 9pm to 7am&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role we have will enable you to make a positive impact using your valuable skills and experience. You will also gain job satisfaction from the positive effects of your hands-on care.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why work for Apollo Home Healthcare?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in the provision of highly complex clinical care services delivered in the homes of service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are passionate about delivering the highest standard of care and we recognise that our Nurses, Healthcare Assistants and Support Workers are integral to doing this. In return for your hard work and dedication you will receive:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible hours to suit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmed rotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent rates of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holiday pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full clinical training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work with other service users in the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing professional training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need key workers on the front line supporting our service users in the fight against the COVID-19 Pandemic.&lt;/p&gt;
